NK030(a)003:1: // gnyis pa nang dbang gi chu bo las /
NK030(a)003:2: mdo dbang gi khro bo'i mngon rtogs /
NK030(a)003:3: khro bo'i dbang gi cho ga'o //
NK030(a)003:4: de nas khro bo'i lha tshogs bskyed pa la /
NK030(a)003:6: e las chos 'byung gru gsum pa mthing nag /
NK030(a)003:7: rgya 'khyon nam mkha' dang mnyam pa /
NK030(a)003:8: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor sra zhing mkhregs pa kha dog duhkha dbyibs rdo rje rgya gram //
NK030(a)003:9: bam las khrag gi rgya mtsho rba brlabs 'khrugs pa dbyibs zlum po /
NK030(a)003:10: mam las sha chen gyis gzhi sra zhing 'thas pa dbyibs pa gru bzhi /
NK030(a)003:11: kam las kem rus kyis ri rab kha khyer dang rgya mnyam pa /
NK030(a)003:13: khrag gi rol mtsho bdun mtsho chen la /
NK030(a)003:16: mtha'i lcags ri dang bcas pa /
NK030(a)003:17: ri rab kyi steng du ram las me'i dkyil 'khor phyed dmar spros pas rlung gi'oda zer dang 'dres /
NK030(a)003:18: me rlung tshubs ma yar byung ba las //
NK030(a)003:19: me ri'i gur khang dmar po /
NK030(a)003:21: rdo rje'i gur khang mthing nag  /
NK030(a)003:22: 'og gzhi rdo rje brag gi steng du /
NK030(a)003:23: sna tshogs rdo rje rgya gram /
NK030(a)003:28: lte ba mthing nag leb mo gru bzhi /
NK030(a)003:29: zur la bang rim bzhi bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK030(a)003:30: de nas gzhal yas khang rnams ni /
NK030(a)003:31: b+h+r+aum s+pha ra na phatah sam ha ra na h'uh
NK030(a)003:32: b+h+aum b+hi shwa b+hi shud d+he b+han d+ha dz+ny+aa na
NK030(a)003:33: / tsakra s+aur+yatsana tra pad+ma e ka man+dala la /
NK030(a)003:36: ru tra kro d+hi ti ra bam /
NK030(a)003:38: sangs rgyas zhing khams thams cad khyab /
NK030(a)003:39: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su dgongs /
NK030(a)003:40: byang chub sems dpa'i spun du dgongs /
NK030(a)003:41: ma mo dang mkha' 'gros rje bor dgongs /
NK030(a)003:42: gzhal yas khang gi che ba'i yon tan thams cad snang ba'i tshul gyis bsdus ste /
NK030(a)003:43: b+h+r+aum la thim 'od du zhu ste /
NK030(a)003:44: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK030(a)003:45: gru bzhi la sgo bzhi pa /
NK030(a)003:46: phyi nang bcu rim du yod pa /
NK030(a)003:47: de yi dri ra ga'i rtsigs pa /
NK030(a)003:50: phyi skam po las rtsigs pa /
NK030(a)003:51: sha chen dang raka ta'i rtsigs 'jim /
NK030(a)003:52: thod pa'i dpral ba nas rdo rje'i thog 'phro ba /
NK030(a)003:58: pan tsa ra ga'i rtsigs pa /
NK030(a)003:64: rmang dang rtse mo phyir ngom pa /
NK030(a)003:65: de rgyab e rag gi rtsigs pa /
NK030(a)003:69: byang ral gri ljang khu gzugs brnyan gyis tshul du 'char ba /
NK030(a)003:70: rtse rtsig phyir ngom pa'i steng du /
NK030(a)003:71: thod pa'i pha gu ser po bzhi gnyis sna gcig non /
NK030(a)003:72: de'i nang ngos la 'dod snams dmar po /
NK030(a)003:74: zhing gi bka' gdung bcu drug dang /
NK030(a)003:75: rtsib ma'i bkrag rtsi bres pa /
NK030(a)003:76: ka thung bcu drug gis gam du mchod pa'i lha
NK030(a)003:77: mo bcu drug gis mchod rdzas du ma thogs pa
NK030(a)003:78: / ka gdung gi steng du gza' chen brgyad kyi
NK030(a)003:79: dmar po gru bzhir bres pa'i phyi ngos la thod
NK030(a)003:80: skam gyi shar bu bsgrigs pa /
NK030(a)003:81: nang lha rnams kyi phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du /
NK030(a)003:82: sa bdag sbal pa ser po brgyad kyi ka gdan /
NK030(a)003:83: de'i steng du lha chen brgyad kyi ka ba /
NK030(a)003:84: nyi zla'i ka zhu dang bcas pa brgyad btsugs pa /
NK030(a)003:85: de'i steng du klu chen brgyad kyi gdung ma bzhi zur du bres pa'i steng nas /
NK030(a)003:86: phyi'i mdzes gdung gi thog du /
NK030(a)003:87: rgyu skar nyer brgyad kyis bres pa'i kha nas /
NK030(a)003:88: sbrul nag gi dra ba la dril bu g.yer kha dang /
NK030(a)003:89: rgyu ma la dril bu tshon 'chang ba /
NK030(a)003:90: dra khug gi sbrul mgos tsit+ta'i phol phyings 'dzin pa'i steng du nyi zla'i gdan bting ba /
NK030(a)003:91: gnod sbyin nyer brgyad kyis cham 'thud byas /
NK030(a)003:92: de'i steng du zhing bran gyi dral grab rtsig gshog gi sa tshags /
NK030(a)003:95: de'i steng du rdo rje'i mo gyo ring yug tu
NK030(a)003:96: song pa'i rtse mor pad+ma phyed pa mar 'phyang ba
NK030(a)003:97: / pho gyo ring yug tu song pa'i rtse mor mchod rten /
NK030(a)003:104: zur bzhir gnam lcags kyi gzer chen gdab pa /
NK030(a)003:105: des ni lha rnams nang ma khebs pa'o //
NK030(a)003:106: de'i steng du ka thung gi kha la /
NK030(a)003:107: mdzes gdung gru bzhir bres pa /
NK030(a)003:108: nang pad khar rtsigs pa gru bzhi'i steng du gdung zlum bres pa /
NK030(a)003:109: gdung zlum gyi steng nas mdzes gdung gi kha la
NK030(a)003:110: phyam nyi shu rtsa bzhi bres pa'i kha la dra
NK030(a)003:112: rdo rje'i gyo ba la sogs kyi gru chad bzhi bakababa pa /
NK030(a)003:113: de'i steng du phyi ka gdung gi kha la mdzes gdung gru bzhir bres pa'o /
NK030(a)003:114: nang bad dkar rtsigs pa zlum po'i kha la gdung ma gru bzhir bres pa /
NK030(a)003:115: de'i thog du phyam nyu shu bres pa'i kha la dra ba la sogs dang /
NK030(a)003:118: de'i steng du phyi ka thung gi kha la mdzes gdung gru bzhi bris pa'o //
NK030(a)003:119: nang bad dkar rtsigs pa gru bzhi gting du gdung ma zlum por bres pa /
NK030(a)003:120: de'i steng phyam bcu drug bres pa'i kha la dra ba la sogs dang /
NK030(a)003:121: rdo rje mthing nag gi gyo mo las gyes rtsibs bzhi bkab pa'o //
NK030(a)003:122: de'i steng du bum gdan gru bzhi /
NK030(a)003:124: bre ske dang bre gru bzhi chos 'khor dang gdugs zlum /
NK030(a)003:125: dar 'phyangs nyi zla rdo rje tog dang bcas pa'o //
NK030(a)003:126: de ni 'khyams dang po'i rim pa'o /
NK030(a)003:128: / 'khyams dgu po kun la phyi rtsigs pa nas /
NK030(a)003:131: lha rnams kyi nang zur nas ka ba phyogs bzhi
NK030(a)003:132: mtshams su gtsugs pa'i thog tu gdung gru bzhir bres
NK030(a)003:133: pa'i steng du phyam nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi kha
NK030(a)003:134: la dra ba la sogs dang /
NK030(a)003:135: rdo rje gyo sogs kyis lha rnams bkab pa dang /
NK030(a)003:136: de nas rim bzhin du bang rim bzhi dang /
NK030(a)003:137: bum pa bzhi la sogs pa'ang nang dang mthun par gsal ba /
NK030(a)003:138: mchod rten gyi nang du mchod rten bcu ba rtsig pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)003:139: rgyal chen pho mos sgo skyes byas pa /
NK030(a)003:142: zhing phran la sbrul nag gis sgo srog byas pa'i sgo leb /
NK030(a)003:144: sgo thog du bcu gcig rdo rje'i dra mig /
NK030(a)003:145: sgo khang nang gis rgyan dgu dang bcas pa'o //
NK030(a)003:146: sgo them gyi phyi rgyab tu /
NK030(a)003:147: stegs rta babs bang rim bzhi bzhi /
NK030(a)003:148: sgo khang gi phyi zur bzhi nas ka ba bzhi bzhi'i kha la //
NK030(a)003:149: glang gur dang bcas pa brgyan rta babs bang rim bzhi bzhi pad+ma dang bcas pa la /
NK030(a)003:151: de'i steng du yu ba chos 'khor bcu gsum dang bcas pa'i zhing lpags kyi gdugs /
NK030(a)003:153: nyi zla rdo rje'i tog dang bcas pa'o //
NK030(a)003:154: chos 'khor g.yas g.yon du 'brug gi ri dwags gnyis gnyis 'brug sgra sgrogs pa'o //
NK030(a)003:155: gzhal yas khang gi phyi rol du /
NK030(a)003:156: dur khrod chen po brgyad kyis bskor ba'o //
NK030(a)003:157: gzhal yas khang gi nang 'khor lo'i lte ba dang /
NK030(a)003:159: rin po che'i khri la sogs pa'i gdan drug ba
NK030(a)003:160: rtsegs gzhan rnams la rang rang gi gdan bsam mo
NK030(a)003:161: // de nas lha bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)003:162: a kra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)003:163: ka ta ma ha kro ti shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK030(a)003:165: che mchog sku mdog mthing nag dbu nyer gcig ste /
NK030(a)003:169: de'i steng dbus ser g.yas gnyis ljang dmar g.yon gnyis mthing dkar /
NK030(a)003:175: rtse mo dmar po rta dbu ljang kus rta skad bsgrogs pa /
NK030(a)003:176: phyag zhe gnyis kyi dang po gnyis kun bzang yab yub thugs khar bsnol nas 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:189: yi dwags dmyal ba'i thub pa nyi shu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:191: dpal chas brgyad gyis brgyan pa /
NK030(a)003:193: me ri me dpung gi klong na bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)003:194: byol song bco brgyad kyi khri la //
NK030(a)003:195: dregs pa pad zla nyi ma'i steng du /
NK030(a)003:196: yum khro mo rnam zhal ma sku mdog mthing nag
NK030(a)003:197: dbu dgu'i dbus ma mthing ka'i zhal che mchog gi
NK030(a)003:198: gsang ba'i rdo rje dang sbyor ba /
NK030(a)003:201: che mchog zhabs g.yas pa bzhi dang sbyor ba /
NK030(a)003:205: dmar gyi zhal bzhi che mchog zhabs g.yon pa bzhi dang sbyor ba /
NK030(a)003:206: phyag bco brgyad kyi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang thod pa thugs kar bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:207: g.yas kyi 'og ma brgyad kyi gnas ma brgyad kyi lha mo brgyad bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:208: g.yon gyi 'og ma brgyad kyi yul ma phra men brgyad bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:209: gnas ma brgyad dang yul ma brgyad kyis thod pa bcu drug bsnams pa'ang snang ngo //
NK030(a)003:210: zhabs bzhi nyi ma la sogs pa'i gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK030(a)003:211: dpal dang dur khrod kyi chas la sogs pa yab dang 'dra ba la /
NK030(a)003:212: gzig gis sham thabs can gsal bar bskyed do //
NK030(a)003:213: badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)003:214: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri sa ma ya h+aum /
NK030(a)003:215: che mchog yab yum gyis mdun du /
NK030(a)003:216: badz+ra he ru ka mthing nag /
NK030(a)003:221: phyag dang po gnyis thugs khar rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK030(a)003:222: g.yas 'og ma gnyis kha tam dang rnge'u chung /
NK030(a)003:223: g.yon 'og ma gnyis thod khrag dang rnga yab /
NK030(a)003:224: yum sngo skya g.yas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK030(a)003:225: g.yon thod khrag yab la stobs pa /
NK030(a)003:226: dom gyi gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK030(a)003:227: me dpung gi klong na bzhugs pa'o //
NK030(a)003:228: bud+d+ha sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)003:229: bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:230: shar rtsibs la bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum smug nag g.yas dkar g.yon dmar /
NK030(a)003:231: phyag dang po gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bu thugs khar bsnol ba /
NK030(a)003:232: g.yas 'og ma gnyis pad+ma dang rtse gsum //
NK030(a)003:233: g.yon 'og ma gnyis ban dmar sdig mdzub /
NK030(a)003:234: khyu mchog gi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)003:235: rat+na sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)003:236: rat+na kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:238: rat+na he ru ka ser nag /
NK030(a)003:240: phyag dang po gnyis rin chen dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)003:241: g.yas 'og ma gnyis rtse gsum dang ral gri /
NK030(a)003:242: g.yon 'og ma gnyis b+han dmar dang ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:243: dregs pa ma he'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)003:244: pad+ma sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)003:245: pad+ma kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK030(a)003:247: pad+ma he ru ka dmar nag /
NK030(a)003:249: phyag dang po gnyis pad+ma dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)003:250: g.yas 'og ma gnyis dgra s+t+wa dang rtse gsum //
NK030(a)003:251: g.yon 'og ma gnyis thod khrag dang ral gri /
NK030(a)003:252: stag gi gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK030(a)003:253: karma sh+ri he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK030(a)003:254: kar+m+aa kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK030(a)003:256: karma he ru ka ljang nag /
NK030(a)003:258: dang po gnyis rgya gram dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)003:259: g.yas 'og ma gnyis rtse gsum dang gshol /
NK030(a)003:260: g.yon 'og ma gnyis b+han dmar dang ti ra bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:261: dregs pa khyo shugs gzig gi gdan la bzhugs pa //
NK030(a)003:262: yum thams cad sku mdog yab dang 'dra ba /
NK030(a)003:264: g.yon pa thod khrag yab la stobs pa /
NK030(a)003:265: yab yum kun dpal chas dang /
NK030(a)003:266: dur khrod brgyad kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK030(a)003:267: ma h+aa raka sha he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK030(a)003:268: sarba du sh+tan ta ka ha na da ha pa
NK030(a)003:269: tsa h+aum phata / ma h+aa rak+sha kro ti shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK030(a)003:271: raka sha he ru ka mthing nag /
NK030(a)003:272: dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa zhal dang po gsum dbus mthing /
NK030(a)003:274: de'i steng ma gsum dbus smug /
NK030(a)003:278: dbus mthing g.yas dkar g.yon dmar /
NK030(a)003:279: phyag bac+wa brgyad kyi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dung dmar bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)003:280: g.yas 'og ma brgyad na dgra s+t+wa /
NK030(a)003:281: g.yon 'og ma brgyad na mdung rtse gsum /
NK030(a)003:282: yum raka sha he ru ka dung khrag stobs pa dang 'khril ba /
NK030(a)003:283: dregs pa bsnol ba'i gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK030(a)003:284: ma h+aa rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK030(a)003:285: sarba dush+ta na ta ka ha na da ha pa
NK030(a)003:286: tsa h+aum phata / ma h+aa yak+sha kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK030(a)003:288: yak+sha he ru ka mthing nag yab yum zhal dbus ma mthing /
NK030(a)003:291: phyag dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)003:292: g.yas 'og ma gnyis rtse gsum dang rnga chung /
NK030(a)003:293: g.yon 'og ma gnyis ral gri dang sta re /
NK030(a)003:294: yum gzig sham dregs pa bsnol pa'i gdan la //
NK030(a)003:295: ma h+aa sa nu sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa
NK030(a)003:296: tsan d+ha sarba du sh+tan ta ka ha da ha
NK030(a)003:298: ma h+aa sa nu kro ti shwa ri dza la h+aum phata /
NK030(a)003:300: sa nu he ru ka dmar nag g.yas dkar g.yon sngo /
NK030(a)003:301: dang po gnyis rdo rje dang thod khrag /
NK030(a)003:302: g.yas 'og ma gnyis rtse gsum dang rnga chung /
NK030(a)003:303: g.yon 'og ma gnyis ban dmar dang kha tam kha /
NK030(a)003:304: g+hu ya sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)003:305: g+hu ya kro ti shwa re s+t+wam /
NK030(a)003:307: g+hu ya he ru ka ljang nag /
NK030(a)003:310: phyag dang po gnyis ral gri dang ban dmar bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)003:311: bar ma gnyis gtun shing dang rtse gsum /
NK030(a)003:312: tha ma gnyis glang chen lpags pa gsol ba /
NK030(a)003:313: dregs pa'i gdan la yum sngar bzhin no //
NK030(a)003:315: shar gyi glo 'bur la ko r+ai ma dkar mo //
NK030(a)003:318: zhing lpags kyi na bza' stod du g.yog pa /
NK030(a)003:323: zhabs ga dub la sogs pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK030(a)003:327: tso ri ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa /
NK030(a)003:329: nub kyi glo 'bur la pra mo dmar mo /
NK030(a)003:330: g.yas chu srin gyis rgyan mtshan /
NK030(a)003:334: be t+aa l+ai nag mo g.yas rdo rje /
NK030(a)003:335: g.yon zhing zhal du gsol ba /
NK030(a)003:339: phyag g.yon pas zhing bsnams nas /
NK030(a)003:340: g.yas pas de'i rgyu ma zhags pas 'dren pa /
NK030(a)003:341: badz+ra g+ha sa ma r+ai h+aa /
NK030(a)003:342: lho nub kyi gru chad la /
NK030(a)003:343: g+hasma ri ljang khu g.yon pas thod khrag g.yas pa rdo rjes dkrug cing gsol pa /
NK030(a)003:345: nub byang gi gru chad la /
NK030(a)003:347: phyag gnyis kyis zhing bzung la /
NK030(a)003:350: byang shar du gtum mo ser mo /
NK030(a)003:351: phyag gnyis kyis zhing bzung nas mgo lus bral ba'o //
NK030(a)003:352: badz+ra sing ha mu kh+ai hi /
NK030(a)003:353: 'khyams dang po'i lha snams dang po shar du /
NK030(a)003:354: sir ha mu kh+ai ser mo /
NK030(a)003:355: mgo seng ge dkar mo'i kha nas ro za ba /
NK030(a)003:356: phyag gnyis kyi rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgya thugs kar bsnol ba /
NK030(a)003:357: badz+ra bya g+h+ri mu kh+ai he /
NK030(a)003:358: lhor bya g+h+ri mu kh+ai dmar mo stag mgo ser mo /
NK030(a)003:359: phyag gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgya thugs kar bsnol ba /
NK030(a)003:360: badz+ra sring+ga la mu khi hi /
NK030(a)003:361: nub tu sring+ga la mu khe nag mo wa ser po'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:362: phyag gnyis kyi zhing gi lpags pa bsnams nas de'i chu ser ldag pa /
NK030(a)003:363: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+ai he /
NK030(a)003:364: byang du sho na mu khi 'thing nag spyang ka'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:365: phyag gnyis zhing bzung nas de'i glo snying za ba'o //
NK030(a)003:367: shar lhor g+r+aing d+ha mu kh+ai dmar mo bya rgod dkar po'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:370: badz+ra kam ka mu kh+ai he /
NK030(a)003:371: lho nub tu kam ka mu ki sku mdog dmar mo /
NK030(a)003:372: phyag gnyis kyis zhing phrag pa la khur ba /
NK030(a)003:373: badz+ra kam ka mu kh+ai ha //
NK030(a)003:374: nub byang du kha kha mu kh+ai nag mo /
NK030(a)003:377: badz+ra u lu mu kh+ai he //
NK030(a)003:378: byang shar du hu lu mu khi mthing kha 'ug pa ser po'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:379: g.yas lcags kyu g.yon thod khrag /
NK030(a)003:380: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dza /
NK030(a)003:381: shar sgor rta gdong lcags kyu ma dkar mo rta'i gdong can /
NK030(a)003:385: lho sgor phag gdong zhags pa ma ser mo /
NK030(a)003:388: nub sgor sprel gdong dmar mo lcags sgrogs bsnams pa'i
NK030(a)003:389: mdo mig smin mtshams su yod pa'i nang ma nyi
NK030(a)003:390: zla ga'u nang du rnal 'byor ba'i tshe 'dzin pa
NK030(a)003:391: / badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya b+ha to ho /
NK030(a)003:392: byang sgor spyang gdong ma ljang khu //
NK030(a)003:393: g.yas dril bu g.yon thod khrag bsnams pa //
NK030(a)003:394: brgyan cha lugs gong dang mthun pa'o /
NK030(a)003:396: badz+ra a pra ti ha a r+ya ni tsa tu ra ta ra phata /
NK030(a)003:399: mi zad sna tshogs mdog g.yas nyi zer g.yon zhags pa /
NK030(a)003:401: lhor gtum mo ser mo mdung bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:403: nub rdo rje mtshon me ma dmar mo g.yas dril bu g.yon thod khrag /
NK030(a)003:405: byang du thog med ma sngo nag /
NK030(a)003:408: shar lhor me khyer ma dmar nag /
NK030(a)003:411: lho nub gshin rje ma sngo nag ral gri dang dgra sta bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:414: gnod sbyin mo mthing nag khyung thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:416: byang shar du 'jigs rten ma smug nag /
NK030(a)003:418: sh+r+ai badz+ra mut+ga ra mu kha shwa ra ya ya na ma h+aum /
NK030(a)003:419: shar sgor mig gcig ma dkar mo //
NK030(a)003:420: rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:421: sh+ri badz+ra ra ga ma shwa ra y+aa ya na ma h+aum /
NK030(a)003:422: lho sgor tshe 'phel ma ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa //
NK030(a)003:423: sh+ri kha tam kha pra dz+wa la ya ya na ma h+aum /
NK030(a)003:424: nub sgor dmar mo dbang sdud ma /
NK030(a)003:425: chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:426: sh+ri badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa la ya ya na ma h+aum /
NK030(a)003:427: byang sgor ljang nag ral gcig ma /
NK030(a)003:428: gsung rab dril bu khrol ba /
NK030(a)003:430: shar stod nas rim pa ltar ma drug bskyed /
NK030(a)003:431: ma nu raka sha si b+h+yo /
NK030(a)003:432: dbang phyug chen mo mi srin mo /
NK030(a)003:433: sku mdog dmar nag rdo rje dang thod rlon bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:435: mi srin ma dmar ser g.yag gi mgo can /
NK030(a)003:436: zhing chen dang tri shul bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:438: tshangs ma sku mdog dmar ser /
NK030(a)003:441: tshangs ma dmar skya sbrul mgo can /
NK030(a)003:442: rtse lnga dang ban dmar bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:444: 'khrug mo sku mdog dkar mo rdo rje dang tri shul bsnams pa //
NK030(a)003:445: de nyid gnas gyur pa khro mo dmar ser gzig mgo can /
NK030(a)003:448: dbang mo ma sku mdog dkar mo in tra gdeng ba dang /
NK030(a)003:450: de nyid gnas gyur pa in tra dkar dmar sre mong mgo can /
NK030(a)003:454: rtog 'dod ma sngon mo rdo rje dang 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:456: khyab 'jug ser mo pha wang gi mgo can 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:458: gzhon nu ma dmar mo rdo rje dang mdung bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:459: de nyid gnas gyur pa dbang mo dmar skya /
NK030(a)003:460: dred kyi mgo can bam dbyug bsnams pa //
NK030(a)003:466: zhi ba dmar mo sku mdog dmar mo dom gyi mgo can /
NK030(a)003:469: bdud rtsi ma sku mdog dmar mo rdo rje dang pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:471: bdud rtsi ma sngon mo chu srin gyi gdong pa can /
NK030(a)003:472: rin po che'i bum pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:474: zhi ba ma sku mdog dkar mo /
NK030(a)003:475: rdo rje dang pun+d+ha ri ka bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:477: zhi ba mo sngo skya sdig pa'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:478: bam ril khog smad bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:480: be con ma sku mdog sngon mo rdo rje dang dbyug to 'phyar ba /
NK030(a)003:482: be con nag mo khra'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:483: bam chen gyi thod rlon bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:485: srin mo sku mdog dmar ser rdo rje dang thod khrag /
NK030(a)003:487: srin mo dmar nag wa'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:490: za ba mo sku mdog dmar nag rdo rje dang ba su 'dren pa /
NK030(a)003:492: za byed nag mo stag gi mgo can dang /
NK030(a)003:496: dga' ba mo sku mdog dkar mo /
NK030(a)003:497: rdo rje dang ga dar bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:499: dga' byed dmar mo bya rgod kyi mgo can /
NK030(a)003:501: badz+ra ru ti ri ma ti b+h+yo /
NK030(a)003:502: khrag 'thung myos ma sku mdog dkar mo /
NK030(a)003:503: rdo rje dang gshol bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:505: khrag 'thung dmar nag rta'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:506: rdo rjer dbyug dang dung dmar bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:507: badz+ra e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK030(a)003:508: rdo rje ser mo rdo rje dang spu gri /
NK030(a)003:510: gcig pu dkar dmar lding gi mgo can /
NK030(a)003:511: rdo rje dang ban d+ha bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:512: am ma nu ha ram b+h+yo /
NK030(a)003:513: yid 'phrog ma sku mdog dmar mo /
NK030(a)003:516: yid 'phrog dmar ser khyi'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:519: grub mo sku mdog dkar mo rdo rje dang bum pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:521: gru mo dkar dmar pu shud kyi mgo can /
NK030(a)003:522: pad+ma dang byi snying za ba /
NK030(a)003:524: rlung mo sku mdog sngo nag /
NK030(a)003:525: rdo rje dang ba dan 'phyar ba /
NK030(a)003:527: rlung mo dmar skya sha ba'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:530: badz+ra ma h+aa ma ra na b+h+yo /
NK030(a)003:531: khyo med ma sku mdog dmar nag rdo rje dang ral gri /
NK030(a)003:533: gsod byed ljang nag sbyang khu'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:534: bam chen dang rnga chung 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:536: me lha mo sku mdog dmar mo rdo rje dang gsal shing 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:538: me long ljang dmar skyiin gyi mgo can /
NK030(a)003:539: sreg rgyu 'dren pa badz+ra b+aa ra hi b+h+yo /
NK030(a)003:540: sna chen ma sku mdog dmar nag /
NK030(a)003:541: rdo rje dang thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK030(a)003:543: sna chen ljang dmar glang gi mgo can /
NK030(a)003:544: bam chen la longs sbyod pa /
NK030(a)003:546: chu lha mo sku mdog dkar mo sngo sbrul zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:547: de nyin gnas gyur pa las /
NK030(a)003:548: klu mo ljang nag sbrul mgo can /
NK030(a)003:549: bdud rtsi dung dmar gsol ba /
NK030(a)003:551: gnyis shar sgor nag mo sku mdog nag po /
NK030(a)003:552: rdo rje dang lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:553: de nyid gnas gyur pa nag mo khu byug gi mgo can dang /
NK030(a)003:555: badz+ra ma h+aa ka la ye b+h+yo /
NK030(a)003:556: lho sgor ra mgo ma sku mdog dmar ser zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:557: de nyid kyi sprul pa ra gdong ma /
NK030(a)003:558: sngon mo ra mgo can zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:559: badz+ra bum pa ka la ma b+h+yo /
NK030(a)003:560: nub tu bum sna ma sku mdog sngo nag lcags sgrogs bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:561: de'i sprul pa be con ma dmar mo /
NK030(a)003:565: byang sgor pus 'dzin ma sku mdog ljang nag rdo rje dang dril bu 'khrol ba /
NK030(a)003:566: de'i sprul pa gsus 'dzin ma ljang dmar /
NK030(a)003:568: dril chen dang dung dmar bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:569: de ltar dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad po kun /
NK030(a)003:572: dar dang rin chen brgyan kyis brgyan pa /
NK030(a)003:574: zhing skam tshal pa'i gdan dang bcas pa'o //
NK030(a)003:575: de nas 'khyams sgo bzhi pa'i mkha' 'gro ma sum bcu rtsa gnyis la /
NK030(a)003:583: mkha' 'gro dga' byed dkar mo rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:584: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:587: badz+ra ma h+aa he la ba ti h'u /
NK030(a)003:588: bsod byed ma dkar mo mda' gzhu 'gengs ba /
NK030(a)003:589: ku ma ra pra ye h'u /
NK030(a)003:590: spor byed dkar skya spu gri bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:591: ma h+aa badz+ra ma ti h'u /
NK030(a)003:592: 'bar byed ma mthing nag rin chen bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:593: badz+ra tri sh+r+ai sma ra ya h'u /
NK030(a)003:597: khro gnyer ma mthing nag 'phyar dar 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:598: ma h+aa badz+ra kro d+hi h+aum /
NK030(a)003:599: 'joms byed ma mthing kha mchu 'grams zhing kha gdangs bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:600: ma h+aa a smri tot+pa ti h'u /
NK030(a)003:602: pad+ma dang thod khrag bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:607: 'khor lo ma dmar ser 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:608: ma h+aa ra ma ni h'u /
NK030(a)003:610: lce dang lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:611: ma h+aa a smri ti ka pa la hasti ta ki h'u /
NK030(a)003:612: sna tshogs lus 'chang ma ljang khu rgya gram dang s+t+wa re bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:614: bsrung ba mo ljang khu go khrab /
NK030(a)003:615: badz+ra smri ta su ta dan+da ri h'u /
NK030(a)003:617: mche ba dang sgrom bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:619: yang dag 'phrog byed ma ljang khu /
NK030(a)003:620: rdo rje khu tshur bsnams pa b+hi b+ha ri ram h'u /
NK030(a)003:621: bya rog gdong ma nag mo /
NK030(a)003:622: dri dang mkhar gzhong bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:624: 'jig byed ma dkar sngo mche ba gtsigs ma dkar mo /
NK030(a)003:625: rin chen dang dung dmar 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:626: badz+ra sha ni ta ka h'u //
NK030(a)003:627: thams cad sgrol byed dkar sngo gzhad kyi mgo can /
NK030(a)003:630: las byed ma dkar sngo 'ug pa'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:633: dur khrod 'joms ma khyi'i mgo can mthing nag kem rus 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:635: rtog bral ma mthing nag phag mgo can /
NK030(a)003:638: 'dod 'joms ma sngo nag rnga mo'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:640: ta ki bi ka te thon dbyug ma sngo mo /
NK030(a)003:641: bong bu'i mgo can dgra s+t+wa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:642: badz+ra ti ra shi ta h'u /
NK030(a)003:644: / 'joms ma dmar mo ra'i mgo can /
NK030(a)003:647: k+aa li pra be sha h'u /
NK030(a)003:648: sgrol byed ma dmar nag byi la'i mgo can //
NK030(a)003:651: zhe sdang 'jom byed ma dmar ljang //
NK030(a)003:653: kem rus dang mi mgo 'dzin pa //
NK030(a)003:655: kun rdzogs ma dmar ser lce spyang gi mgo can /
NK030(a)003:658: srin mo bum sna dmar ser seng ge mgo can /
NK030(a)003:659: rdo rje dang lcags kyu bsnams pa //
NK030(a)003:664: d+ha sha g+h+ri wa ljang nag /
NK030(a)003:666: lcags sgrogs dang dril bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:667: badz+ra s+aa b+han a ki h'u /
NK030(a)003:669: dril bu dang dgra sta bsnams pa'o //
NK030(a)003:670: thams cad thod pa skams rlon zhing lpags gzig la sogs khro bo'i rgyan chas du mas brgyan pa'o //
NK030(a)003:671: sgo 'khyams lnga pa'i phyogs bzhir ma bdun /
NK030(a)003:672: sgo bzhir sring mo bzhi ste /
NK030(a)003:673: ma ma d+ha du kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:674: rdo rje kun drag ma dmar sngo ri rab thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:675: ma ma da du kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:676: kun tu bzang mo dmar ma nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:677: ma ma da du kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:678: rdo rje kun grags ma sngon mo //
NK030(a)003:680: ma ma da du kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:681: rdo rje ye shes ma dmar mo //
NK030(a)003:683: ma ma da du kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK030(a)003:684: rdo rje 'od chags ma sngon mo //
NK030(a)003:685: rdo rje dra ba'i phreng ba thogs pa //
NK030(a)003:686: ma ma da du kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:687: rdo rje 'od 'phro ma sngon mo zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:688: ma ma da du kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:689: rdo rje g.yu sgron ma dmar mo //
NK030(a)003:690: ral gri dang thod khrag bsnams pa //
NK030(a)003:693: gling bzhi 'gyogs ma lha'i sring mo dkar mo /
NK030(a)003:694: bya rgod kyi rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:695: rgod thul gsol ba badz+ra dun ting b+h+yo /
NK030(a)003:696: mkha' la khyung lding gshin rje'i sring mo ser mo stag gi rgyal mtshan dang /
NK030(a)003:699: dmar mo g.yag thod klu'i sring mo //
NK030(a)003:700: chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa //
NK030(a)003:701: chu srin gyis thul ba gsol ba //
NK030(a)003:703: nag mo sder chen gnod sbyin gyi sring mo /
NK030(a)003:705: rma bya'i thul pa gsol ba'o //
NK030(a)003:706: sgo 'khyams drug pa ging chen bac+wa brgyad bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)003:707: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ra h+aum /
NK030(a)003:708: dpal chen las kun byed mthing nag ral gri dang /
NK030(a)003:709: b+han d+ha thogs pa badz+ra ka tar+shi shwa ra h+aum /
NK030(a)003:710: khro mo khams gsum dbang bsdud ma sngo nag /
NK030(a)003:711: thod khrag dang ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:712: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:713: rdo rje ka tar ging ka ra dmar nag b+han d+ha dang ga tar 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:714: badz+ra ka ti ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:715: rdo rje ging chen gnod sbyin ljang nag /
NK030(a)003:717: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ra h+aum /
NK030(a)003:718: rdo rje ging chen spyang ki dmar nag spyang gdong can /
NK030(a)003:720: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:721: rdo rje ging chen ya ma mthing nag be con dang dgra sta bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:722: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:723: rdo rje ging chen rol pa dmar nag /
NK030(a)003:724: b+han d+ha dang phal tshab bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:725: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:726: rdo rje ging chen 'chi bdag ljang ser /
NK030(a)003:728: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:729: rdo rje ging chen dus mtshams ljang nag /
NK030(a)003:730: shag ti b+han d+ha bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:731: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:732: rdo rje ging chen ro langs ser nag zhing gi dbyug pa //
NK030(a)003:733: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:734: rdo rje ging chen 'joms pa smug nag /
NK030(a)003:735: rdo rje tho ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:736: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:737: rdo rje ging lcags dbang bsgyur ma /
NK030(a)003:738: lcang nag rdo rje dang lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:739: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h'u /
NK030(a)003:740: rdo rje ging lcam dbang bsgyur ljang nag lcags kyu bsnams pa //
NK030(a)003:741: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:742: rdo rje ging lcam 'phrul mo dmar mo zhing lag na thod pa bsnams pa'o //
NK030(a)003:743: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ra h+aum /
NK030(a)003:744: rdo rje ging lcam glog 'gyu ma /
NK030(a)003:745: rdo rje dang pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:746: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:747: rdo rje ging chen mthu mo che /
NK030(a)003:748: ljang nag lcags kyi tho ba bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:749: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:750: rdo rje ging lcam rtsam mo che //
NK030(a)003:751: mthing nag rdo rje dang dgra sta thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:754: rdo rje ging lcam bsgrol byed ma /
NK030(a)003:755: smug nag b+han d+ha dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:758: rdo rje ging lcam za byed ma /
NK030(a)003:759: ljang nags lcags kyu dang ban d+ha bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:760: de thams cad stag sham dang gzig sham la sogs khro bo dang /
NK030(a)003:761: khro mo'i rgyan du mas brgyan pa'o //
NK030(a)003:762: sgo 'khyams bdun pa steng gi khro bo khro mo drug cu ste /
NK030(a)003:763: shar du khro bo yab yum drug /
NK030(a)003:768: steng 'og gnyis na gnyis ste drug cu gsal bar bskyed de /
NK030(a)003:769: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:770: rnam par rgyal ba dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum phyag g.yas rdo rje /
NK030(a)003:772: yum snye ma dkar mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK030(a)003:773: g.yon pas thod khrag yab la stobs pa /
NK030(a)003:774: gnyis ka dri za'i gdan la bzhengs pa'o //
NK030(a)003:775: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:776: khro bo dbyug sngon can sngon po'i rin chen dang sdig mdzub /
NK030(a)003:777: yum rdo rje sder mo me lha'i gdan la bzhengs pa //
NK030(a)003:778: kro ta kro ri shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:779: khro bo gshin rje gshed mthing nag /
NK030(a)003:781: yum dur khrod bdag mo thod pa //
NK030(a)003:782: gshin rje'i gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK030(a)003:783: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:784: mi g.yo ba ser dmar ral gri dang //
NK030(a)003:786: rdo rje gtun khung ma thod pa srin po'i gdan la /
NK030(a)003:787: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK030(a)003:788: rta mgrin dmar po mda' gzhu dang pad+ma /
NK030(a)003:790: klu'i gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:791: khro bo gzhan gyi mi thub pa sngo ljang khu //
NK030(a)003:792: dgra sta dang gtun shing bsnams pa //
NK030(a)003:793: yum mda' snyems ma thod pa //
NK030(a)003:795: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:796: bdun rtsi 'khyil pa ljang nag rgya gram bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:798: gnod sbyin gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:799: khro bo khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba nag po rdo rje dang tho ba /
NK030(a)003:801: dbang ldan gyis gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:802: khro bo stobs po che dud kha rnga yab thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:804: sa gdon gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:805: khro bo h+aum mdzad dmar skya mda' gzhu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:807: nyi zla gza' skar rnams gdon gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:808: badz+ra ki la mthing nag phur pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:810: dgra dang lha gdon gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:811: rme rtsegs mthing nag rdo rje bsnams pa //
NK030(a)003:813: bdud dang ru tra'i gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:816: yag mo dung dmar rmu gdon gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:817: khro chen dmar nag rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:818: khro mo dbang bsgyur ma dung dmar /
NK030(a)003:819: mo gdon gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:820: khro bo za 'og ljang khu sbrul bsnams pa //
NK030(a)003:821: khro mo za 'og mo thod khrag /
NK030(a)003:822: smu gdon gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK030(a)003:823: khro bo rab 'khrug sngon po ral gri bsnams pa //
NK030(a)003:824: khro mo rab 'jigs ma thod khrag /
NK030(a)003:825: gdon chen bac+wa brgyad kyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:826: ma h+aa ka la dmar nag zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:827: khro mo ral sgreng ma thod khrag /
NK030(a)003:828: ya bdud kyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK030(a)003:831: khro mo 'joms byed ma dung dmar sri can gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /

NK030(a)003:1167: go gyon nas bdud dpung 'joms pa /
NK030(a)003:1168: ha la ha la p+aa sha h'u /
NK030(a)003:1169: pho nya sdud byed ma dmar mo /
NK030(a)003:1170: 'gro ba'i tshe 'phrog nas gar byed pa /
NK030(a)003:1171: ha la ha la p+aa sha h'u /
NK030(a)003:1172: pho nya bla 'dzin ma dmar ser /
NK030(a)003:1173: dgra bo'i bla bkug nas 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1174: ha la ha la p+aa sha h'u /
NK030(a)003:1176: ser smug lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1177: ha la ha la p+aa sha h'u /
NK030(a)003:1178: pho nya rtsa dkrol ma ser mo /
NK030(a)003:1179: sum rgya drug cu'i rtsa ba la rgyu ba /
NK030(a)003:1180: ha la ha la p+aa sha h'u /
NK030(a)003:1181: pho nya gnas 'byin ma ser smug  /
NK030(a)003:1183: sa dgu gting nas 'joms par byed pa /
NK030(a)003:1184: ha la ha la p+aa sha h'u /
NK030(a)003:1185: pho nya gnas stod ma ser mo /
NK030(a)003:1186: sems can thams cad thar lam la 'god par mdzad pa'o /
NK030(a)003:1189: dgra dang klu gdon 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK030(a)003:1190: nub phyogs 'od zer dmar po las /
NK030(a)003:1191: zangs kyi mi mo drug bcu ste //
NK030(a)003:1192: gar rdza gar rdza s+pho ta bam /
NK030(a)003:1193: gsung gi pho nya thog 'phen ma /
NK030(a)003:1195: gar rdza gar rdza s+pho ta bam /
NK030(a)003:1196: gsung gi pho nya 'brug sgrogs ma /
NK030(a)003:1198: ga rdza gardza s+pho ta bam /
NK030(a)003:1199: gsung gi pho nya char 'bebs ma /
NK030(a)003:1200: sprin chen glog pa gsol ba /
NK030(a)003:1201: ga rdza gsung gi pho nya 'od 'gyed ma /
NK030(a)003:1202: dmar nag 'ja' tshon gyi nang na bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)003:1203: gardza pho nya bkrag gsal ma dmar nag g.yu'i lan 'phran can /
NK030(a)003:1204: gardza pho nya 'ja' tshon ma dmar nag  /
NK030(a)003:1205: 'ja' tshon gyi zhags pa thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1206: gardza pho nya 'od 'phro ma dmar nag nyi ma'i zer 'phro ba /
NK030(a)003:1207: gardza pho nya 'od gsal ma dmar nag me 'od phyag bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1208: gardza pho nya khrag 'thung ma dmar nag /
NK030(a)003:1210: gardza pho nya dbang phyug ma dmar nag /
NK030(a)003:1212: gardza pho nya sa bdag ma dmar sngo //
NK030(a)003:1213: lcags kyi phag mgo thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1216: rdo rje lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1217: gardza pho nya dkar sham ma /
NK030(a)003:1218: dmar sngo bse'i go zu can /
NK030(a)003:1219: gardza pho nya sgrogs ma dmar sngo zhing gi rnga chung brdung ba //
NK030(a)003:1220: gardza pho nya yid gzhung ma /
NK030(a)003:1222: lag gnyis khu tshur bcangs pa /
NK030(a)003:1223: gardza pho nya lta na mdzes dmar sngo /
NK030(a)003:1230: mi thod dang rta mgo thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1231: gardza pho nya 'gyogs byed ma dmar sngo khyung chen chibs su chibs pa //
NK030(a)003:1232: gardza pho nya gsod byed ma dmar sngo dung thogs cing seng ge la zhon pa /
NK030(a)003:1233: gardza pho nya snying 'byin ma dmar ljang tsit+ta thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1234: gardza pho nya dmar 'thung ma ljang dung khrag 'thung ba /
NK030(a)003:1235: gardza pho nya rkang 'jibs ma dmar ljang /
NK030(a)003:1237: zas su rkang dang bcud 'jibs pa //
NK030(a)003:1238: gardza pho nya las byed ma dmar ljang 'brug sngon chibs su 'acibasa pa /
NK030(a)003:1239: gardza pho nya zhags thogs ma sngon mo /
NK030(a)003:1240: zhags pa thogs pa rlung la zhon pa /
NK030(a)003:1241: gardza pho nya zla 'phrog ma dmar ljang /
NK030(a)003:1242: skyi bser gyi rta la zhon pa /
NK030(a)003:1243: gardza pho nya thogs med ma dmar ljang /
NK030(a)003:1244: ral gri rnon po thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1245: gardza pho nya za byed ma dmar mo /
NK030(a)003:1246: stag la zhon pa gtsang rme med pa za ba /
NK030(a)003:1247: gardza pho nya myos byed ma dmar ljang lcags kyi tho ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1248: gardza pho nya smug byed ma dmar ljang //
NK030(a)003:1249: lcags kyi dra ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1250: gardza pho nya rdzu byed ma dmar ser /
NK030(a)003:1251: ra skyes khams pa la zhon pa /
NK030(a)003:1252: gardza pho nya 'khrugs byed ma dmar ser /
NK030(a)003:1254: gardza pho nya drag mo dmar ser gtum po dom la zhon pa /
NK030(a)003:1255: gardza pho nya skem ma dmar ser khrag gi lan phran can /
NK030(a)003:1256: gardza pho nya 'jom ma dmar ser bya spang rta'i mgo can //
NK030(a)003:1258: gardza pho nya rab dga' ma dmar ser lag na zangs gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1259: gardza pho nya 'dzin ma dmar ser sbrul zhags bsnam pa /
NK030(a)003:1260: gardza pho nya glog 'gyu ma dmar ser /
NK030(a)003:1262: gardza pho nya g.yul 'joms ma dmar ser lag na shaka ti thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1264: dmar ser rdo rje'i thogs 'bebs pa /
NK030(a)003:1266: dmar smug ka ta ra bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1267: gardza pho nya myur byed dmar smug glog gi zhags pa can /
NK030(a)003:1268: gardza pho nya rings byed ma bud med lus la mchu mo che //
NK030(a)003:1269: ri lung med par rjes kyi 'gengs pa /
NK030(a)003:1270: gardza pho nya srog byed ma dmar smug lag na gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1271: gardza pho nya glog byed ma dmar smug rdo rje dang be con bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1272: gardza pho nya tho ba ma dmar smug rdo rje tho ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1273: gardza pho nya gtun khung ma dmar smug lag na gtun khung thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1274: gardza pho nya zhags 'phen ma dmar smug bdud kyi zhags pas gang la dmigs 'dzin par byed pa /
NK030(a)003:1275: gardza pho nya me khyer ma dmar smug dur khrod kyi mes phyi nang bsreg par byed pa /
NK030(a)003:1276: gardza pho nya sdud byed ma dmar smug gser gyi phreng ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1277: gardza pho nya g.yengs byed ma dmar skya //
NK030(a)003:1279: gardza pho nya bdud 'joms ma dmar skya gtun dang tho ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1280: gardza pho nya dpal mo srid pa'i dpal 'phrog par
NK030(a)003:1281: byed pa dmar skya lcags kyu gser g.yu spel ma'i
NK030(a)003:1283: gardza pho nya dbang phyug ma dmar skya //
NK030(a)003:1284: rdo rje rtse gsum dang thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK030(a)003:1285: gardza pho nya grags pa mo dmar skya //
NK030(a)003:1287: gardza pho nya gtum bag can dmar smug /
NK030(a)003:1288: dgra bo'i snying 'byin cing cho nge 'debs pa /
NK030(a)003:1289: gardza pho nya ka la yangs pa dmar skya ka li'i mtshon thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1290: gardza pho nya bde tshogs ma dmar skya //
NK030(a)003:1291: pad khrag khrag gis char 'babs pas /
NK030(a)003:1292: ma mo 'bum sde bran du 'khol ba /
NK030(a)003:1293: gardza pho nya ha la'i gdong /
NK030(a)003:1294: dmar skya bdud rtsi thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1295: gardza pho nya rab brjid ma dmar skya /
NK030(a)003:1296: mi mgo rnam gsum gyis 'phreng ba sbreng zhing glad
NK030(a)003:1297: la bskor bas dgra bgegs la rgyal bar mdzad pa'o
NK030(a)003:1298: // dgra dang gnod sbyin 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK030(a)003:1300: / 'jigs byed pho nya sku sprul pa /
NK030(a)003:1301: byang phyogs 'od zer sngon po las //
NK030(a)003:1302: g.yu'i mi mo drug bcur sprul /
NK030(a)003:1303: pa tsa pa tsa g+ha n+d+ha ho /
NK030(a)003:1304: he sha d+ha ra sa ma y+aa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)003:1305: las kyi pho nya mo ljang nag /
NK030(a)003:1306: rdo rje rgya gram thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1307: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+d+ha ho /
NK030(a)003:1308: e sha d+ha ra sa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)003:1309: 'phrin las kyi pho nya 'joms ma chen mo /
NK030(a)003:1310: ljang sngon khyung gi khra thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1311: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+d+ha ho /
NK030(a)003:1313: 'phrin las kha lo bsgyur bar mdzad ma ljang sngon dred kyi g.yang gzhi rdeb pa /
NK030(a)003:1314: pa tsa pa tsa pho nya dbang phyug ma ljang sngon thod rlon khrag gi gang ba bsnams pa //
NK030(a)003:1316: pa tsa pa tsa pho nya 'gug byed ma ljang sngo mi mag dung du 'bud pa /
NK030(a)003:1317: pa tsa pho nya bskul byed ma ljang sngon /
NK030(a)003:1319: pa tsa pho nya grub pa mo ljang sngon g.yu'i 'khor lo 'chang ba /
NK030(a)003:1320: pa tsa pho nya mthar phyir ma ljang khu g.yu'i thor tsug can /
NK030(a)003:1322: pa tsa pho nya mthar byed ma ljang khu /
NK030(a)003:1323: rdo rje rgya gram thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1324: pa tsa pho nya chud mi za ba ljang sngon dung gi mche ba 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1325: pa tsa pho nya dbang bsgyur ma ljang dmar /
NK030(a)003:1326: chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1327: pa tsa pho nya thogs med ma /
NK030(a)003:1328: 'dab chags bya'i rgyal po la zhon pa ljang khu /
NK030(a)003:1329: 'jigs su rung ba'i mtshon cha 'phyar ba /
NK030(a)003:1330: pa tsa pho nya grub pa ma ljang dmar shel gyi za ma tog bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1331: pa tsa pho nya gsal byed ma ljang dmar me'i zhags pa 'phen pa /
NK030(a)003:1332: pa tsa pho nya dbang mo che ljang dmar rdo rje lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1333: pa tsa pho nya dam tshig ma ljang dmar /
NK030(a)003:1335: pa tsa pho nya bya ra ma lcags kyi spyang khu g.yu'i mig can /
NK030(a)003:1338: pa tsa pho nya stangs 'dzin ma ljang dmar /
NK030(a)003:1339: rtsibs kyi byang bu thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1340: pa tsa pho nya stangs gcod ljang dmar brtsis kyi khram thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1341: pa tsa las kyi pho nya gsal 'dzin ma dmar ljang /
NK030(a)003:1343: pa tsa pho nya bskul byed ma ljang ser /
NK030(a)003:1345: pa tsa pho nya dbang mo ljang ser khrag gi phor ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1346: pa tsa pho nya phag mo ljang ser /
NK030(a)003:1348: pa tsa pho nya spyan brgya mo mgo lus med par mig gis gang ba /
NK030(a)003:1349: pa tsa pho nya mig stong ma dbu stong /
NK030(a)003:1353: 'ja' tshon gyi lus la 'od kyi mig /
NK030(a)003:1354: bltas pas mi mthong ba gang yang med pa /
NK030(a)003:1355: pa tsa pho nya rlung zhon ma ljang khu la ga na lcags kyi dgra s+t+wa thogs pa //
NK030(a)003:1356: rlung nag 'tshub ma la zhon pa /
NK030(a)003:1357: pa tsa pho nya rdzu 'phrul can ljang ser /
NK030(a)003:1358: sbrul nag stong gi zhags pa 'phen pa //
NK030(a)003:1359: ltas ngan rnga mong gwa pa la zhon pa /
NK030(a)003:1360: pa tsa pho nya rgyu ba mo cir yang ma
NK030(a)003:1361: nges gzugs su ston pa re 'ga' chu srin sbrul
NK030(a)003:1362: gyis yu ba spu gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1363: pa tsa pho nya dbang phyug rgyal ljang ser //
NK030(a)003:1365: pa tsa pho nya drag rgyal mo ljang nag /
NK030(a)003:1366: dred kyi mgo can stag la zhon pa gri thod /
NK030(a)003:1367: pa tsa pho nya dpal bsham ma ljang nag dmar gyi gtor ma glad la bskor ba /
NK030(a)003:1368: khrag gi gtor ma'i zhags pa 'phen pa /
NK030(a)003:1369: pa tsa pho nya yaka sha mo ljang nag gnod sbyin gyi mgo thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1370: pa tsa pho nya khro bag can /
NK030(a)003:1371: bud med kyi lus la skyes pa'i mgo /
NK030(a)003:1374: pa tsa pho nya mche ba can /
NK030(a)003:1375: lag gnyis rdo rje mche ba 'debs pa /
NK030(a)003:1376: pa tsa las kyi pho nya dbang skur ma /
NK030(a)003:1377: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya can /
NK030(a)003:1378: pa tsa pho nya dngos grub bdag mo ljang nag 'dod yon lnga la rol ba /
NK030(a)003:1379: pa tsa pho nya sgrol byed ma chen po ljang nag gcod pa'i phal tshab thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1380: pa tsa pho nya mnga' bdag mo ljang nag rnga chung brdungs ba /
NK030(a)003:1381: pa tsa pho nya 'od 'phro ma ljang nag /
NK030(a)003:1383: pa tsa pho nya drag mo ljang nag gru gsum mthing nag thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1384: pa tsa pho nya khros skyes ma ljang smug glo nag sa la brdeb pa /
NK030(a)003:1385: pa tsa pho nya myur 'grub ma ljang dpal sngon po lag na ral gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1386: pa tsa pho nya chud ma zos ma //
NK030(a)003:1387: ljang smug rin chen me sgron thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1388: pa tsa pho nya 'dul byed ma ljang smug /
NK030(a)003:1389: srin po'i thod pa thod pa /
NK030(a)003:1391: sna tshogs lus 'chang rgya mtsho skyom pa /
NK030(a)003:1392: pa tsa pho nya ltung 'dzin ma /
NK030(a)003:1394: pa tsa pho nya sgrol byed ma dmar smug /
NK030(a)003:1396: pa tsa pho nya kun gnyen ma ljang smug g.yu'i zhags pa 'debs pa /
NK030(a)003:1397: pa tsa pho nya 'dul mkhan mo /
NK030(a)003:1398: skyes bu na chung gi gzugs 'chang ba /
NK030(a)003:1399: pa tsa pho nya goms pa mo ljang khu dug gi mda' 'phen pa /
NK030(a)003:1400: snying dkar nag gi mtshams su brdeg pa /
NK030(a)003:1401: pa tsa pho nya las mkhan ma ljang skya mche ba'i zor 'phen pa /
NK030(a)003:1402: pa tsa pho nya dbang sgyur ma nyi zla gza' skar gyis slog pa gyon pa /
NK030(a)003:1403: gling bzhi lag na thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1404: pa tsa pho nya mchog sgrol ma ljang skya mchog gi tsit+ta 'byin pa /
NK030(a)003:1405: pa tsa pho nya rgyug 'dzin ma ljang khu /
NK030(a)003:1406: shel dang long thang gi spu bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1407: pa tsa pho nya rngams pa mo ljang skya sha khrag rlon pa za ba /
NK030(a)003:1408: pa tsa pho nya so skyes ma ljang skya 'debs pa'i las la myur ba /
NK030(a)003:1409: pa tsa pho nya gtum mo ljang skya /
NK030(a)003:1410: nyi ma dang zla ba'i 'khor lo 'phen pa /
NK030(a)003:1411: pa tsa pho nya mig dmar ma ljang skya //
NK030(a)003:1412: khrag chang gi myos par byed pa /
NK030(a)003:1413: mig rtsa dmar ba ra'i gdong pa can /
NK030(a)003:1414: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+d+ha ho /
NK030(a)003:1415: e sha ra ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)003:1416: 'phrin las pho nya sen mo can dmar smug sen
NK030(a)003:1417: mo lcags kyus bsgral ba'i zhing bcu 'dzin par byed
NK030(a)003:1419: 'og gi ma mo drug bcu bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)003:1420: khams gsum srid gsum thams cad kyi //
NK030(a)003:1421: dgra dang 'byung po bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK030(a)003:1423: ma mo las byed drug bcur sbrul /
NK030(a)003:1427: tri shul dang nad rkyal thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1429: ma mo spal mo thal mdog /
NK030(a)003:1431: dur khrod rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK030(a)003:1433: dur khrod tshogs kyi ral can ma /
NK030(a)003:1438: khrag ral gos su gon pa /
NK030(a)003:1439: phyag gi skye 'gro'i tsit+ta bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1440: ma ma khams gsum sdud pa'i mtshan ma dmar mo //
NK030(a)003:1442: ma ma rgyu drug sgrol ba'i ma chen mo /
NK030(a)003:1445: mi snying dang rus 'phreng glad la bskor ba /
NK030(a)003:1446: ma ma srid gsum za byed ma /
NK030(a)003:1448: gnam sa gnyis kyi gos gon pa /
NK030(a)003:1449: ma ma snang srid yongs la dbang bsgyur ma //
NK030(a)003:1450: ser nag nyi zla'i thod bcings pa /
NK030(a)003:1451: gnam sa gnyis la dbang byed ma /
NK030(a)003:1452: ma ma mthu rtsal snyems ma ljang nag zhing gi go zu gsol ba /
NK030(a)003:1453: lag pa g.yas kyis nam mkha' 'degs pa /
NK030(a)003:1454: ma ma sha khrag gsur la dga' ba ma /
NK030(a)003:1455: mi sha rta sha zas su za ba /
NK030(a)003:1456: mi khrag rta khrag skom du 'thung ba /
NK030(a)003:1457: ma ma sgrol byed ma chen mo /
NK030(a)003:1458: mthing nag nang 'khrol blo snying 'byin pa /
NK030(a)003:1459: ma ma za byed chen mo sngo nag g.yu'i za ma tog bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1460: ma ma rngam byed ma ser nag 'brug sngon 'chibs su bcibs pa /
NK030(a)003:1461: dgra dang nyams pa'i snying 'byin pa /
NK030(a)003:1462: ma ma 'dzin byed chen mo ser nag thod khrag dang lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1463: ma ma bgegs chen 'joms ma sngo nag spu gri dang tho ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1464: ma ma zhing bcu sgrol byed ma ljang nag b+han d+ha dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1465: ma ma chad pa gcod pa'i mi mo sngon nag zhing gi g.yang gzhi brdeb pa dang /
NK030(a)003:1467: ma ma 'byung po sgrol byed ma /
NK030(a)003:1468: b+han d+ha dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1469: ma ma gshin rje sgrol byed ma b+han+ha dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1470: ma ma klu sgrol byed ma //
NK030(a)003:1471: b+han d+ha dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1472: ma ma gnod sbyin sgrol byed ma ljang nag b+han+da dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1473: ma ma srin mo bsgrol byed ma chen mo sngo nag b+han+ha dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1474: ma ma srin mo bsgrol byed chen mo smug nag /
NK030(a)003:1476: ma ma gzugs la dbang ba'i dbang mo /
NK030(a)003:1477: dkar mo zhing gi dbyug pa thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1478: ma ma khrag ma dbang ba'i dbang mo sngon mo thod khrag dkrugs cing 'thung ba /
NK030(a)003:1479: ma ma drod la dbang ba'i dbang mo /
NK030(a)003:1480: dmar mo lag na tsit+ta bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1481: ma ma dbugs la dbang mo ljang nag thod khrag dang zhags pa thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1482: ma ma bkrag mdangs la dbang ba'i dbang mo ser nag ral gri dang thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK030(a)003:1483: ma ma srog la dbang ma smug nag gri dang thod khrag bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1485: khrag 'thung ma bya rgod mgo ser ljang ral gri dang thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK030(a)003:1486: ma ma ma mo za byed stag gi mgo can dmar ser thod khrag gsol ba /
NK030(a)003:1487: ma ma ma mo 'jigs byed ma /
NK030(a)003:1488: chu srin gyi mgo can khrag gsol ba /
NK030(a)003:1489: ma ma ma mo dur khrod rgyan byed ma //
NK030(a)003:1490: mi lpags rlon pa'i na bza' gsol ba /
NK030(a)003:1492: ma ma gar gyi dbang mo /
NK030(a)003:1493: dbu rgyan spyan stong dang ldan pa'o //
NK030(a)003:1494: ma ma pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug ma /
NK030(a)003:1495: lag na mi mgo'i phor ba'i nang du /
NK030(a)003:1496: mi snying tshil bus bkang nas gsol ba /
NK030(a)003:1497: ma ma sa bdag pad+ma phreng ba dmar nag phyag na b+han d+ha khrag gi bkang gsol ba /
NK030(a)003:1498: ma ma srid gsum bdag mo /
NK030(a)003:1499: g.yas ri rab rtse gsum nas brnyil bar byed pa /
NK030(a)003:1500: g.yon rgya mtsho'i gting nas rnyog par byed pa /
NK030(a)003:1501: ma ma rgya mtsho'i gting gi mthu mo che //
NK030(a)003:1502: chu srin lpags pa'i na bza' gsol //
NK030(a)003:1503: sbrul nag 'bum gyi gdengs ka can //
NK030(a)003:1504: ma ma ma mo rdo rje tho ba mo /
NK030(a)003:1505: sngo nag rdo rje tho ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)003:1506: ma ma ma mo rdo rje gtun khung ma /
NK030(a)003:1507: mthing nag dgra bo gtun tu brdung bar byed pa /
NK030(a)003:1508: ma ma rdo rje dur khrod bdag mo sngon nag mi mgo rdo rje dbyug pa gdengs ba /
NK030(a)003:1509: ma ma rdo rje sring mo sngo nag /
NK030(a)003:1511: ma ma rdo rje gsal bkra dmar nag /
NK030(a)003:1513: ma ma rdo rje khrag 'thung ma ljang nag /
NK030(a)003:1514: b+han d+ha rak+tasa bskang ba gsol ba /
NK030(a)003:1515: ma ma nag mo drel zhon ma /
NK030(a)003:1516: nad kyi rkyal pa gang du rtags pa /
NK030(a)003:1517: mtshon gyis gru gu glad la bskor ba /
NK030(a)003:1519: srid pa gsum la dbang byed cing /
NK030(a)003:1520: sku cir yang bsgyur bar byed pa /
NK030(a)003:1521: ma ma ma mo gnas nyul ma /
NK030(a)003:1522: spyang khu'i mgo can mi sha za ba /
NK030(a)003:1523: ma ma ma mo rdzu byed ma stag dang dom dang /
NK030(a)003:1524: gcan gzan gdug pa'i gzugs su sprul pa /
NK030(a)003:1525: ma ma 'dzum byed pho nya ma /
NK030(a)003:1528: ma ma gnam sa phyed kyi bdag mo ri lung med par gzugs gyis kheb pa /
NK030(a)003:1529: che chung med par 'joms par byed pa /
NK030(a)003:1530: ma ma ma mo rgyug byed ma /
NK030(a)003:1531: bud med lus la 'ja' tshon gyi gos gon pa /
NK030(a)003:1532: ma ma pho nya za byed ma bud med kyi lus la stag gis gos gon pa /
NK030(a)003:1533: zas su gtsang rme med par za ba /
NK030(a)003:1534: ma ma rdo rje ya byin ma /
NK030(a)003:1535: dkar khra lcags kyu dang phur bu 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1536: ma ma rdo rje bse sbyin rtsal mo che /
NK030(a)003:1539: ma ma rdo rje de byin dbang mo che /
NK030(a)003:1540: dmar mo rdo rje lcags sgrogs dang phur bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1541: ma ma rdo rje phag byin ma ljang nag rdo rje dril bu dang /
NK030(a)003:1543: ma ma sa bdag rgyal mo ser nag /
NK030(a)003:1544: gser gyi bum pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1545: ma ma phyi 'khor skyong ba'i bdag mo //
NK030(a)003:1546: brgyan dang cha lugs mdzes pa'i tshul can no //
NK030(a)003:1547: ma ma 'phrog srin rje mo bud med bzang sdug 'od chags ma bkra shis pa /
NK030(a)003:1548: ral ba gyen du bsig pa /
NK030(a)003:1550: khro tshigs myur ba'i ma mo //
NK030(a)003:1551: bud med khrag gi las 'phran can no //
NK030(a)003:1553: bla ma rig 'dzin brgyud pa rnams bskyed de //
NK030(a)003:1554: rdzogs pa chen po'i brgyud pa dang //
NK030(a)003:1555: lung a nu yo ga'i brgyud pa dang /
NK030(a)003:1556: sgyu 'phrul gyi brgyud pa dang gsum shar stod de byang shar nas /
NK030(a)003:1557: byang shar gyi bar du rim pa ltar bskyed /
NK030(a)003:1559: thog mar rdzogs chen brgyud pa ni /
NK030(a)003:1560: chos kun tu bzang po yab yum sku mdog sngon po mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK030(a)003:1561: rus pa dang rin po che'i rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK030(a)003:1562: rin chen la sogs pa'i khri dang pad+ma nyi ma zla ba'i gdan la skyil krung gi bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)003:1563: de'i g.yon du rgyal ba rigs lnga seng ge la sogs pa'i khri sogs spyi dang mthun par bskyed /
NK030(a)003:1564: de'i g.yon du sdud pa po /
NK030(a)003:1566: phyag na rdo rje gnyis spyi dang mthun par bskyed /
NK030(a)003:1567: gu ru mah+aa sha ri ram /
NK030(a)003:1569: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje rab byung gi tshul du gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)003:1570: 'jal dpal bshes gnyen dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa'i tshul /
NK030(a)003:1571: rgyal po d+ha he na ta lo rgyal po'i gzugs /
NK030(a)003:1572: sras ra dza hasti rgyal bu'i gzugs can /
NK030(a)003:1573: sras mo wa ra ni btsun mo'i tshul /
NK030(a)003:1574: klu'i rgyal po 'jog po klu'i tshul /
NK030(a)003:1576: sbrul mgo'i gdeng ka sbrul gyi khri la pad dkyil bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)003:1578: rgyal po'i sras mo gnod sbyin byang chub mo //
NK030(a)003:1579: bud med kyi gzugs can rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1580: smad 'tshong ma a ra li bud med gyi tshul rdo rje 'adzinapa /
NK030(a)003:1581: kha che'i slob dpon a k+sho b+h+yahraba byung gi cha lugs /
NK030(a)003:1582: khyi'i mkhan po ku ku ra dz+aa ras dkar bcings pa /
NK030(a)003:1584: gzung ma smad 'tshong ma bud+d+ha m+aa ti bud med kyi cha lugs rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1585: smad 'tshong ma bud+d+ha sa ma ya /
NK030(a)003:1586: bud med kyi gzugs rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1587: o rgyan rgyal po ma h+aa ra dza ni rgyal bu dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1588: sras mo go ma de byi ni /
NK030(a)003:1589: bud med kyi cha lugs rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1590: +aa tsar+ya a lo ke kha che'i mkhan po rab snang dang gcig yin snyam /
NK030(a)003:1592: dge slong gi cha lugs rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1593: ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma ras dkar dang ber thul /
NK030(a)003:1594: slob dpon ma h+aa ra dza dge slong gi cha lugs rdo rje 'dzin pa //
NK030(a)003:1595: slob dpon drang srong b+ha shi ti /
NK030(a)003:1596: drang srong gcer bu thor gtsug can /
NK030(a)003:1597: smad 'tshong ma bdag nyid chen mo /
NK030(a)003:1598: bud med kyi tshul rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1599: slob dpon n+aa ga rdzu na /
NK030(a)003:1600: dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po /
NK030(a)003:1601: slob dpon de ba r+aa tsa ni /
NK030(a)003:1605: rig 'dzin dge bsnyen legs skyes rab byung gi tshul rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1606: slob dpon d+harma ra tsa dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1607: slob dpon bud d+ha gug ta phu tung dang chos gos can rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1608: slob dpon sh+r+ai seng ha pan chen gyi cha lugs /
NK030(a)003:1609: slob dpon b+hi ma mi tra dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1611: dge slong gi cha byad rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1612: slob dpon be ro tsa na phu rung dang chos gos can rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1613: slob dpon g.yu sgra snying po dge slong gi tshul rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1614: mkhas pa ye shes gzhon nu /
NK030(a)003:1615: sog po dpal gyi ye shes /
NK030(a)003:1617: gnubs khu lung pa nyon yon tan rgya mtsho //
NK030(a)003:1619: mkhas pa nyang can sher mchog /
NK030(a)003:1622: zur chung shes rab grags pa //
NK030(a)003:1624: gsang bdag mda' tsha hor po /
NK030(a)003:1627: de'i sras bla ma thang stong 'bum med /
NK030(a)003:1628: chos rje bla skyabs rdo rje /
NK030(a)003:1629: drin can mkhas grub chen po //
NK030(a)003:1631: ma gcig drin can zur mo //
NK030(a)003:1636: bshes gnyen dkon mchog bzang po /
NK030(a)003:1640: don grub legs pa dpal 'bar rnams dge slong rdo
NK030(a)003:1641: rje 'dzin pa'i cha lugs pa ci ltar 'os bar
NK030(a)003:1642: bsgom / de nas lung a nu yo ga mdo dbang brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)003:1643: rgyal ba kun bzang yab yum sngon mo /
NK030(a)003:1644: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs rigs lnga /
NK030(a)003:1645: sdud pa po 'jam dpal dang phyag na rdo rje /
NK030(a)003:1646: spyan ras gzigs dam pa'i rigs can lnga gong ltar bskyed /
NK030(a)003:1647: de nas dge slong ku ku r+aa tsa /
NK030(a)003:1650: sras mo go ma de byi /
NK030(a)003:1653: slob dpon rdo rje gzhad pa //
NK030(a)003:1656: slob dpon sogs skya de ba /
NK030(a)003:1657: slob dpon sgegs pa rdo rje /
NK030(a)003:1658: slob dpon dz+nya na ku ma ra /
NK030(a)003:1659: sog po dpal gyi ye shes /
NK030(a)003:1660: mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug /
NK030(a)003:1661: slob dpon nam mkha' snying po /
NK030(a)003:1662: slob dpon chos blon de ba /
NK030(a)003:1663: rgya gar mkhan po chos rgyal skyong /
NK030(a)003:1664: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che /
NK030(a)003:1665: khu lungs kyi gnub ston yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK030(a)003:1669: zur chung shes rab grags pa /
NK030(a)003:1670: chu bar gyi glan sh+aakya bzang po /
NK030(a)003:1672: sreg ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK030(a)003:1677: 'gos ston pa bsod nams grags pa /
NK030(a)003:1678: yang na glan rdo rje 'od nas /
NK030(a)003:1682: glan ston chos kyi seng ge /
NK030(a)003:1690: bla ma dkon mchog bzang po /
NK030(a)003:1694: sprul sku don grub dpal 'bar legs pa rnams dge slong rdo rje 'dzin par bsgom mo /
NK030(a)003:1695: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga sgyu 'phrul brgyud pa'i bla ma bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)003:1696: chos sku kun bzang yab yum /
NK030(a)003:1697: longs sku rgyal ba rigs lnga //
NK030(a)003:1698: sdud pa po rigs gsum mgon po /
NK030(a)003:1699: dam pa'i rigs can lnga ste /
NK030(a)003:1700: ma h+aa sha ri ram gi li h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1702: gser mdog nor bu bsam 'phel 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1703: phyed skyil dkrung du bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)003:1704: ma h+aa sha ri ram gi li h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1707: thal mo sbyar ba'i bar du nor bu 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)003:1708: ma h+aa sha ri ram gi li h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1709: rig 'dzin gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong /
NK030(a)003:1710: dkar ser phyed dkyil rin po che'i sgrom bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)003:1711: ma h+aa rig 'dzin lang ka mgrin bcu /
NK030(a)003:1712: dkar smug skra bardzisa ro'i gdan la rkyang skum du bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)003:1713: ma h+aa rig 'dzin rgyal po li tsa byi /
NK030(a)003:1714: rab byung gi tshul skyil krung gi bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)003:1715: ma h+aa ku ku r+aa dza /
NK030(a)003:1718: rgyal po u pa ra dza /
NK030(a)003:1719: sring mo go ma de w+air /
NK030(a)003:1720: khyi'i rgyal po ku ku r+aa dza /
NK030(a)003:1721: ro langs bde ba'i dngos grub /
NK030(a)003:1725: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba /
NK030(a)003:1728: mkhas pa gtsug gyer rnam gnyis /
NK030(a)003:1731: khu lugs yon tan rgyal mtsho /
NK030(a)003:1733: myang shes rab mchog myang ye shes 'byung gnas /
NK030(a)003:1742: dpal ldan chos kyi seng ge /
NK030(a)003:1752: bshes gnyen dkon mchog bzang po /
NK030(a)003:1753: rig 'dzin chos kyi rje rdo rje bzang po /
NK030(a)003:1756: rgyal ba don grub legs pa dpal 'bar rnams phal
NK030(a)003:1757: chen dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa sha stag tu
NK030(a)003:1758: bsgom mo // lha tshogs de dag rnams la ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK030(a)003:1759: sku gsung thugs kyis byin gyis brlabs /
NK030(a)003:1760: sa ma dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK030(a)003:1762: dza h+aum bam hos ba stim /
NK030(a)003:1763: ka ya wa ka tsi tas brtan par byas /
NK030(a)003:1764: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK030(a)003:1765: sgrub dang gdug ba 'dul ba yis /
NK030(a)003:1767: / 'bar ba khro bo'i lha tshogs la /
NK030(a)003:1768: sgo gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)003:1779: glu ye shes rnams dbyangs dang bcas pas zhi khro ltar /
NK030(a)003:1781: rgya mtshor lnga'i smon lam gdab //
NK030(a)003:1784: h+aum tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi /
NK030(a)003:1786: / 'khor lo 'bar ba dbus kyi lte ba la //
NK030(a)003:1787: bcom ldan dpal chen che mchog he ru ka /
NK030(a)003:1788: ston pa kun tu bzang po gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1789: rgyal ba khro rgyal kun gyi rje btsan yab //
NK030(a)003:1790: che ba'i nang na yang che bla na med //
NK030(a)003:1791: che btsan 'gran zla bral ba kun gyi mchog /
NK030(a)003:1792: sku gsung thugs kyis bdag la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK030(a)003:1794: / 'bar ba'i dbu ni nyi shu rtsa gcig gis //
NK030(a)003:1795: sa ni nyi shu rtsa gcig rim pas mnan //
NK030(a)003:1796: g.yas g.yon phyag ni bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis na //
NK030(a)003:1797: rgyal ba sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bzhugs //
NK030(a)003:1798: zhabs brgyad bsgrad pas khro mo'i dbu brgyad bardzisa //
NK030(a)003:1799: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer sku la brjid //
NK030(a)003:1800: dpal gyi chas brgyad dur khrod brgyan rnams rdzogs //
NK030(a)003:1801: che mchog he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1802: kun tu bzang mo chos nyid gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1803: dpal 'bar khro mo kun gyi rje btsun yum //
NK030(a)003:1804: shes rab dbyings nas sku bskyed thugs rjer ldan //
NK030(a)003:1805: khro mo rnam zhal ma la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK030(a)003:1808: a kra ma h+aa kro ti sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1809: ka ta ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1810: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1812: h+aum bcom ldan dbang mchog he ru ka /
NK030(a)003:1814: dbu gsum dang por byung ba ni //
NK030(a)003:1815: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK030(a)003:1816: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i dbu //
NK030(a)003:1817: khams gsum mya ngan 'das pa'i zhal //
NK030(a)003:1818: dbu gsum bar du rngam pa ni //
NK030(a)003:1819: g.yas sngo g.yon ljang dbus mthing zhal //
NK030(a)003:1820: thabs dang shes rab sems kyi dbu //
NK030(a)003:1821: srid gsum dbyings su rdzogs pa'i zhal //
NK030(a)003:1822: dbu gsum thog mar rngam pa ni //
NK030(a)003:1823: g.yas mthing g.yon mthing dbus mthing zhal //
NK030(a)003:1824: lung dang man ngag sems kyi dbu //
NK030(a)003:1825: khams gsum re ba bskong pa'i zhal //
NK030(a)003:1826: bco brgyad phyag rgya rol ba ni //
NK030(a)003:1827: stong pa bac+wa brgyad dbyings su thim //
NK030(a)003:1828: bac+wa brgyad phyag rgya bsnams pa ni //
NK030(a)003:1829: rdo rje glo snying zhing chung g.yas //
NK030(a)003:1830: b+han d+ha zhing chung ti ra g.yon //
NK030(a)003:1831: zhing zhags nyi ma khyung chen g.yas //
NK030(a)003:1832: zhing chen zla ba 'ug pa g.yon //
NK030(a)003:1833: me dang rgya mtsho ga bu g.yas //
NK030(a)003:1834: klu dang rin chen ri rab g.yon //
NK030(a)003:1835: yon tan bac+wa brgyad dbyings su rdzogs //
NK030(a)003:1836: khro rgyal brgyan rnams sku la brjid //
NK030(a)003:1837: rgyud rgyal che mchog he ru ka /
NK030(a)003:1838: dbang mchog sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1839: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1840: sarba ta th+aa g+hu h+ya kro ti shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK030(a)003:1841: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum //
NK030(a)003:1842: h+aum dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi /
NK030(a)003:1845: dregs pa bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK030(a)003:1846: bcom ldan mi skyod gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1849: / 'jigs byed chen po'i skur bskyed pa //
NK030(a)003:1850: mchod cing byin brlabs gsal sgrub pa //
NK030(a)003:1851: badz+ra he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1852: nam mkha' kun bzang gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1853: khro mo dbang phyug skur gsal ba //
NK030(a)003:1854: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med //
NK030(a)003:1855: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK030(a)003:1856: badz+ra kro ti sh+ri he ru ka h+aum //
NK030(a)003:1857: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum //
NK030(a)003:1858: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum //
NK030(a)003:1859: h+aum dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yis /
NK030(a)003:1862: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK030(a)003:1863: dri za bsnol ba'i gdan steng na //
NK030(a)003:1864: rnam par snang mdzad gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1868: mchod cing bsgrub te byin rlabs ba //
NK030(a)003:1869: bud+d+ha he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1870: sangs rgyas sbyan ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1871: khro mo dbang phyug skur gsal ba //
NK030(a)003:1872: thabs dang shes rab byang chub sems //
NK030(a)003:1873: spyan drangs mchod cing bsgrub pa'i lha //
NK030(a)003:1874: bud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1876: bud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1877: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1878: h+aum 'bar ba'i 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad kyi //
NK030(a)003:1879: lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK030(a)003:1880: gshin rje bsnol ba'i gdan stengs na //
NK030(a)003:1881: rin chen 'byung ldan gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1885: spyan drangs mchod cing sgrub pa'i lha //
NK030(a)003:1886: rat+na he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1887: h+aum ma ma ki ni gnas gyur pa /
NK030(a)003:1889: / 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur byung pa //
NK030(a)003:1890: yab yum thabs dang shes rab ma /
NK030(a)003:1891: spyan drangs mchod cing bsgrub pa'i lha //
NK030(a)003:1892: rat+na kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1894: rat+na kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK030(a)003:1895: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1896: h+aum dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yis /
NK030(a)003:1899: nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK030(a)003:1900: klu dbang bsnol ba'i gdan stengs na //
NK030(a)003:1901: snang ba mtha' yas gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1904: / 'jigs byed dmar nag ral pa can //
NK030(a)003:1905: spyan drangs mchod cing bsgrub pa'i lha //
NK030(a)003:1906: pad+ma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1907: na bza' dkar mo gnas gyur pa /
NK030(a)003:1909: / 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur byung ste //
NK030(a)003:1910: yab yum thabs dang shes rab la //
NK030(a)003:1911: gnyis med byang chub sems bsgrub pa //
NK030(a)003:1912: pad+ma kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1914: pad+ma kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1915: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum //
NK030(a)003:1916: h+aum dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi /
NK030(a)003:1919: gnod sbyin bsnol ba'i gdan stengs na //
NK030(a)003:1920: don yod grub pa gnas gyur pa /
NK030(a)003:1924: gsal bar byed cing mchog bsgrub pa //
NK030(a)003:1925: karma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1926: dam tshig sgrol ma gnas gyur pa /
NK030(a)003:1928: / 'jigs byed khro mor skur ston pa //
NK030(a)003:1929: lhag ma byang chub sems 'phros pa //
NK030(a)003:1930: yab yum thabs dang shes rab la /
NK030(a)003:1931: kar+m+aa kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1932: kar+m+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1933: kar+m+aa kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1934: ru lu h+aum dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK030(a)003:1935: shar lho 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK030(a)003:1936: mthu stobs mnga' bdag gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1937: sgrol byed chen po bdud rnams 'joms //
NK030(a)003:1938: bdud dang srin po bsgrol la brtson //
NK030(a)003:1939: mthing nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK030(a)003:1940: raka sha he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1941: lha mo raka sha gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1942: khro mo yab kyi cha lugs can //
NK030(a)003:1943: yab yum thabs dang shes rab la //
NK030(a)003:1944: raka sha kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1945: raka sha sh+ri he ru ka /
NK030(a)003:1946: raka sha kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK030(a)003:1947: ru lu h+aum dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yis /
NK030(a)003:1950: lho nub 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)003:1951: badz+ra sa ma ya gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1952: dpal chen dam tshig mnga' mdzad pa //
NK030(a)003:1953: ser nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK030(a)003:1954: bskal pa brgyar yang bdag gi lha //
NK030(a)003:1955: sa nu he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1956: yum chen dam tshig gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1957: khro mo dam tshig bya ra mkhan //
NK030(a)003:1958: sangs rgyas sems can mda' mi byed //
NK030(a)003:1959: dam tshig dbyings su bskul byed ma /
NK030(a)003:1960: sa nu kro ti shwa ri ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1961: sa nu sh+ri he ru ka /
NK030(a)003:1962: sa nu kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK030(a)003:1963: ru lu h+aum dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK030(a)003:1964: nub byang 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs na //
NK030(a)003:1965: mkhyen rab mnga' bdag gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1966: bsgrol byed chen po dregs pa 'dul /
NK030(a)003:1967: ljang nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK030(a)003:1968: dus rnams rtag du gsang ba'i lha //
NK030(a)003:1969: zhe sdang 'khor lo bsgrol la brtson //
NK030(a)003:1970: g+hu ya he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1971: rdzus skyes 'joms ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1972: khro mo yab kyi cha lug 'dzin //
NK030(a)003:1973: yab yum thabs dang shes rab la //
NK030(a)003:1974: g+hu ya kro ti sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1975: g+hu ya sh+ri he ru ka /
NK030(a)003:1976: g+hu ya kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1977: ru lu h+aum dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yis //
NK030(a)003:1978: byang shar 'khor lo rtsibs steng na //
NK030(a)003:1979: thugs rje'i mnga' bdag gnas gyur pa /
NK030(a)003:1982: gang bsgrub mthu dang dbang rtsol ba'i //
NK030(a)003:1983: yaka sha he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK030(a)003:1985: / 'jig rten bdag mo gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)003:1986: khro mo dbang phyug kun gyi rje //
NK030(a)003:1987: sprul pa kun gyis yang sprul ma //
NK030(a)003:1988: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med ma //
NK030(a)003:1989: yaka sha kro ti'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:1990: yaka sha sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK030(a)003:1991: yaka sha kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:1992: ru lu h+aum tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi /
NK030(a)003:1994: / 'bar ba'i glo 'bur gru chad bzhi po nas //
NK030(a)003:1995: ko'u ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams ni //
NK030(a)003:1996: gdug pa thabs kyi 'dul ba'i drag shul can //
NK030(a)003:1997: sku mdog phyag mtshan sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK030(a)003:1998: ye shes khro mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:2007: ru lu h+aum tshogs chen 'dus pa 'bar ba yi //
NK030(a)003:2008: bar 'khyams dang po mdog ser na //
NK030(a)003:2009: seng ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams ni //
NK030(a)003:2010: ye shes las la 'gyed pa'i phra men ma //
NK030(a)003:2011: rnam sbrul las gyi 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK030(a)003:2012: sing ha phra men brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK030(a)003:2013: badz+ra sing ha mu khe he //
NK030(a)003:2014: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu khe he /
NK030(a)003:2015: badz+ra sh+r+ai ga la mu khe he /
NK030(a)003:2016: badz+ra shwa na mu khe he /
NK030(a)003:2017: badz+ra gri d+ha mu khe he /
NK030(a)003:2018: badz+ra kang ka mu kh+ai he /
NK030(a)003:2019: badz+ra kha kha mu khe he /
NK030(a)003:2020: badz+ra u lu ka mu kh+ai he /
NK030(a)003:2021: ru lu bar 'khyams sgo bzhi'i shar lho nub byang bzhir //
NK030(a)003:2022: tshad med bzhi yis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK030(a)003:2023: rta gdong phag gdong seng gdong spyang gdong bzhi /
NK030(a)003:2024: zhi rgyas dbang drag las la thogs med brtson /
NK030(a)003:2025: rtag chad bdag 'dzin mtshan ma lta las grol //
NK030(a)003:2026: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:2027: badz+ra ar+ya te dza te nga dza /
NK030(a)003:2028: badz+ra ba ra ha mu khe h+aum /
NK030(a)003:2030: badz+ra b+ha li sa ma ya ba to ho /
NK030(a)003:2031: ru lu h+aum tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor du /
NK030(a)003:2032: 'bar ba'i bar 'khyams gnyis pa mdog dkar na //
NK030(a)003:2033: chos nyid rnam dag ngang la rang snang ba'i //
NK030(a)003:2034: sna tshogs cir yang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' zhing /
NK030(a)003:2035: srid gsum zhing du sbyor bas ga yang gzhi gsol /
NK030(a)003:2036: spor ma chen mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK030(a)003:2041: ru lu bar 'khyams de'i shar lho /
NK030(a)003:2043: dgyes pa bskyed pa'i gsang ba'i yum chen bzhi /
NK030(a)003:2044: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs sna tshogs 'phro /
NK030(a)003:2045: shes rab yum chen bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK030(a)003:2046: sh+ri badz+ra mu ka ra mu kha shwa ra ya //
NK030(a)003:2047: y+aa na mah sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ma shwa ra
NK030(a)003:2048: ya ya na mah sh+r+ai badz+ra kha t+w+aam ga pra
NK030(a)003:2049: dz+wa la ya ya na mah sh+ri badz+ra g+han+de pra
NK030(a)003:2050: dz+wa la ya y+aa na ma /
NK030(a)003:2051: ru lu tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi /
NK030(a)003:2053: / 'bar ba'i bar 'khyams gsum pa mdog dmar na /
NK030(a)003:2054: srin mo la sogs dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NK030(a)003:2055: dreg pa lha chen rnams kyi chung ma de //
NK030(a)003:2056: dbang drag las la thogs pa med par sbyod //
NK030(a)003:2057: dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:2058: b+h+yo badz+ra ma nu rak+sha si /
NK030(a)003:2059: b+h+yo badz+ra pra ha ma ni /
NK030(a)003:2063: b+h+yo badz+ra in tra ma ni /
NK030(a)003:2071: b+h+yo badz+ra ru d+hi ra ma ti /
NK030(a)003:2072: b+h+yo badz+ra e ka tsa ra ma /
NK030(a)003:2073: b+h+yo badz+ra ma nu ha ram /
NK030(a)003:2076: b+h+yo badz+ra ma h+aa ma ra na /
NK030(a)003:2085: b+h+yo badz+ra lam po d+ha ra /
NK030(a)003:2086: ru lu h+aum tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi /
NK030(a)003:2087: 'bar ba'i bar 'khyams bzhi pa gser mdog na /
NK030(a)003:2088: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing /
NK030(a)003:2090: / 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs cana'aphrula mo che //
NK030(a)003:2091: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyi grogs mdzad ma //
NK030(a)003:2092: mkha' 'gro gsum bcu gnyis la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK030(a)003:2095: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:2096: badz+ra ma h+aa he la ba ti /
NK030(a)003:2099: badz+ra t+r+ai sh+r+ai sma ra ya /
NK030(a)003:2101: ma h+aa badz+ra kro ta h+aum /
NK030(a)003:2102: ma h+aa a smri tod pa ti /
NK030(a)003:2106: ma h+aa a smri ti ka p+aa la hasti ta ki /
NK030(a)003:2108: badz+ra a smri ta su ta dan+da ri /
NK030(a)003:2116: badz+ra dza du la ya ta ki bi ka te /
NK030(a)003:2124: badz+ra sa b+ha na a ki /
NK030(a)003:2125: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK030(a)003:2126: h+aum tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyis /
NK030(a)003:2128: / 'bar ba'i bar 'khyams lnga pa dmar po la /
NK030(a)003:2130: / 'jig rten dregs pa 'dus pa ma mo'i tshogs //
NK030(a)003:2131: phyi 'khor 'dus zhing nang 'khor skyong mdzad pa //
NK030(a)003:2132: dur khrod ma bdun las kyi sring mo bzhi //
NK030(a)003:2133: bgegs bsrungs ma mo rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK030(a)003:2134: ma mo d+ha du kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)003:2138: ru lu ru lu h+aum tshogs ched 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor kyi /
NK030(a)003:2139: 'bar ba'i bar 'khyams drug pa mdog dkar na //
NK030(a)003:2140: khams gsum bsgrol ba'i ging chen bac+wa brgyad ni //
NK030(a)003:2141: srid gsum las la thogs med bsgrol la brtson //
NK030(a)003:2142: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu bstan nas brlagsa par byed //
NK030(a)003:2143: ging chen ging lcam tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:2148: ru lu h+aum tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil gyi /
NK030(a)003:2150: / 'bar ba'i bar 'khyams bdun pa mdog nag na /
NK030(a)003:2151: bcom ldan h+aum mdzad sa gsum brjid kyi gnon /
NK030(a)003:2152: khams gsum 'dul mdzad ye shes lha'i lha /
NK030(a)003:2154: / 'jigs byed 'bar bas gdug pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms //
NK030(a)003:2155: khro bo khro mo'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:2158: ru lu h+aum tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyis /
NK030(a)003:2159: 'bar ba'i bar 'khyams brgyad pa phyogs mtshon na /
NK030(a)003:2160: ye shes thugs rjes phyogs bcur khyab pa yin //
NK030(a)003:2161: gdon bgegs 'dul ba'i las la thogs pa med //
NK030(a)003:2162: ci bgyis bka' nyan las la myur mdzad pa'i //
NK030(a)003:2163: phyogs bzhi pho nya'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:2164: b+ha na b+ha na e sha ra /
NK030(a)003:2166: ha la ha la e sha ra pa sha h+aum /
NK030(a)003:2168: e sha ri s+pho ta bam /
NK030(a)003:2169: pa tsa pa tsa e sha ra g+han+de ho /
NK030(a)003:2170: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK030(a)003:2171: h+aum tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi /
NK030(a)003:2172: 'bar ba'i bar 'khyams dgu pa mdog ljang na /
NK030(a)003:2173: khams gsum yongs su las la dbang ba yi //
NK030(a)003:2174: ma chen rgyal mo srid pa gsum gyis bdag /
NK030(a)003:2175: yum chen las la dbang pa'i dbang mo che //
NK030(a)003:2176: ma mo drug bcu'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)003:2179: ru lu ces rims par bsnyen no //
NK030(a)003:2180: h+aum tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi /
NK030(a)003:2182: / 'bar ba'i bar 'khyams bcu pa mdzes mtshon na //
NK030(a)003:2183: rig 'dzin bla mas byin rlabs ldan pa'i tshogs //
NK030(a)003:2184: lhun grub phyag chen tshe dbang rnam smin gyi //
NK030(a)003:2185: rgya gar bod gyis grub thob ma lus rnams //
NK030(a)003:2186: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi sid d+hi 'dir stsol gcig /
NK030(a)003:2187: gu ru ma h+aa sha ri ram gi li h+aum /
NK030(a)003:2188: ma h+aa gu ru sid+hi hum /
NK030(a)003:2189: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK030(a)003:2192: bdag bskyed dang gsum po des bsnyen bsgrub kyi rim pa de song nas /
NK030(a)003:2193: rab gnas kyi sngon 'gro la sogs don brgyad po ni /
NK030(a)003:2194: gong sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i skabs nas yod pa 'dir blangs la /
NK030(a)003:2196: mdun gyis dkyil 'khor lha rnams dang /
NK030(a)003:2197: gzhan yang tsaka li la sogs dbang rdzas rnams dang /
NK030(a)003:2198: sku gsung thugs gyi rten la sogs dang /
NK030(a)003:2199: slom ma rnams kyang lha zhi khro la sogs par bsgoms la /
NK030(a)003:2202: thog mar zhi ba'i rab gnas byed do //
NK030(a)003:2204: gong sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i skabs na yod pa 'dir blangs la /
NK030(a)003:2205: zhi ba'i sbyin sreg rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg dbang gi sbyin bsreg /
NK030(a)003:2206: drag pa'i sbyin sreg rnams byed do //
NK030(a)003:2207: de yang zhi khro gnyis kyi dbye bas brgyad yod do //
NK030(a)003:2209: sa cho ga gi dus su zhi ba'i sbyin sreg byed /
NK030(a)003:2210: slob bu sta gon gyis dus su /
NK030(a)003:2211: kun gyi rmi lam ngan na drag pa'i sbyin sreg /
NK030(a)003:2213: dbang gi sbyin sreg byed do //
NK030(a)003:2214: de ltar rab gnas sbyin sreg rab gnas rnam pa 'god pa /
NK030(a)003:2217: bdun gyis dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa de song nas /
NK030(a)003:2218: gnyis pa 'jug dbang gi rim pa la /
NK030(a)003:2221: yon tan rnam bcus rgyas shes bya //
NK030(a)003:2222: ces dang dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang /
NK030(a)003:2223: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang //
NK030(a)003:2224: bgegs bskrad lhar rlabs dam tshig sbyin //
NK030(a)003:2225: de nyid dbog dang chu mnan dang //
NK030(a)003:2226: bsgrags dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK030(a)003:2227: lha bab dang nan tan dang //
NK030(a)003:2228: mig dbye dkyil 'khor bstan pa dang //
NK030(a)003:2229: tshogs mchod yon dang rnam bac+wa brgyad /
NK030(a)003:2233: de brtson gsum dang brtul bzhugs gsum //
NK030(a)003:2234: gang la snang ba de yi snod //
NK030(a)003:2237: slob dpon bdag nyid 'jug cing dbang len pa dang /
NK030(a)003:2238: slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK030(a)003:2243: 'jug pa dang gzod par gsol ba'o /
NK030(a)003:2245: dbang phyug gi snyim par me tog gi 'phreng ba thogs te /
NK030(a)003:2246: dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgor gus pas 'dud de dkyil
NK030(a)003:2247: 'khor de nyid 'og min gyi gnas rten dang brten
NK030(a)003:2249: ye shes rgyal pos gsol ba gdab pa /
NK030(a)003:2251: am badz+ra sa ma ya am /
NK030(a)003:2252: h+aum badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK030(a)003:2253: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK030(a)003:2254: ha badz+ra sa ma ya ha /
